Note on the underlying BRIER R package
---------------------------------------

This MCP server is a wrapper around the BRIER R package
(https://github.com/UM-KevinHe/BRIER), which has its own license. The MIT
license above applies only to this MCP wrapper code (the Python server and
the helper R scripts under r_scripts/). When you install and use the BRIER
R package itself, you are bound by that package's license terms; check the
package's DESCRIPTION file or its GitHub repository for the applicable
license. Make sure your downstream use complies with both licenses.
